name: Bradley Vaughn
profile_summary: The user is a 32-year-old man who identifies as straight and uses he/him pronouns. He is a 5'11" White Caucasian and a Taurus. He is comfortable with monogamy and is interested in a long-term relationship. His pets include a dog and a cat. His MBTI personality type is INTJ.
